        <mxCell id="0a1z9_rbOoM-A3mR09Ts-1" parent="ULGAZMTEwaHfj6rt0_g5-1" style="shape=note2;boundedLbl=1;whiteSpace=wrap;size=16;verticalAlign=middle;align=left;fillColor=#fff2cc;strokeColor=#d6b656;html=1;" value="This component represents an abstraction layer over external payment providers&amp;nbsp;(e.g., Stripe, PayPal, Visa).&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;For the purpose of this project, a mock payment gateway is used to simulate&amp;nbsp;real-world scenarios such as successful transactions, failures, timeouts,&amp;nbsp;and network issues.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Security considerations include:&lt;br&gt;- No storage of sensitive card data (e.g., CVV)&lt;br&gt;- Idempotent request handling to prevent duplicate charges&lt;br&gt;- Input validation and error handling&lt;br&gt;- Preparedness for secure webhook validation mechanisms&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;This design allows future integration with real payment providers." vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="214" width="396" x="642" y="14" as="geometry" />
